@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
actor User
participant "Telegram" as TG
participant "Queue Bot\n(main_bot.py)" as Bot
participant "Orchestra REST API" as REST
participant "Orchestra CometD" as CometD

User -> TG: /start, callbacks
TG -> Bot: Updates (long polling)
Bot -> REST: GET /services (branch)
REST --> Bot: services list
Bot -> REST: POST /visits (entry point)
REST --> Bot: ticket

CometD --> Bot: VISIT_CALL event
Bot -> TG: send_message(ticket call)
TG --> User: notification
@enduml
